---
import PageLayout from '../../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
---

<PageLayout
  title="How we built GROOMO.cz"
  description="Case study: the complete creation of the GROOMO.cz brand and Shopify e-shop — from the name and visual identity to unique filtering by dog breed."
  lang="en"
>

  <!-- 2-col layout: sidebar LEFT + content RIGHT -->
  <div class="cs-layout">

    <!-- ROW 1: label + H1 (right column, no nav) -->
    <div class="cs-hero-head">
      <p class="label cs-label">CASE STUDY - BRAND - E-SHOP - COURSE SALES</p>
      <h1 class="cs-h1">How we built<br /><span class="hl-name">GROOMO.cz</span></h1>
    </div>

    <!-- ROW 2 LEFT: sticky nav -->
    <aside class="cs-aside">
      <nav class="page-nav">
        <a href="#s01" class="page-nav-item">01. NAME</a>
        <a href="#s02" class="page-nav-item">02. BRAND</a>
        <a href="#s03" class="page-nav-item">03. E-SHOP</a>
        <a href="#s04" class="page-nav-item">04. INSTITUTE</a>
        <a href="#s05" class="page-nav-item">05. SHOPIFY</a>
        <a href="#s06" class="page-nav-item">06. CONTENT</a>
        <a href="#s07" class="page-nav-item">07. RESULTS</a>
        <a href="#s08" class="page-nav-item">08. GALLERY</a>
      </nav>
    </aside>

    <!-- ROW 2 RIGHT: content -->
    <main class="cs-main">

      <!-- Perex -->
      <p class="cs-perex">Dominika Elliot, an experienced groomer and owner of a successful dog salon, wanted to expand her services with an e-shop. Together we started looking for a way to capture the whole project and how the brand should work.</p>

      <!-- 01 NAME -->
      <section class="cs-section" id="s01">
        <h2 class="h2-mini sec-h2">About the name <a href="https://groomo.cz" class="text-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">GROOMO.cz</a></h2>
        <p class="body sec-text">The brand and the name gave us a hard time. We had to decide between ideas like “psikrasa.cz”, which described what it was about nicely, but didn’t give us much chance to design a logo, and by coming up with something with the English world base of the word GROOMING, even though it’s not a common word and the domains are long gone.</p>
        <p class="body sec-text">Choosing an AI colored dog as an avatar was a similarly controversial move, but in a world of many beautiful dog photographers, we wanted something that would be apart of the ordinary and would say straight away that this wasn’t just an ordinary hobby “dog” from the suburbs.</p>
        <p class="body sec-text">Gradually the colors settled down and we added geometric shapes to give something to build on, for example, social networks, business cards and business cards, and the whole show started.</p>
      </section>

      <!-- 02 BRAND -->
      <section class="cs-section" id="s02">
        <h2 class="h2-mini sec-h2 sec-h2--lav">Brand</h2>
        <div class="brand-logo-grid">
          <div class="logo-cell logo-cell--left">
            <img src="/groomo-logo-imgnavysku-wh.png" alt="GROOMO mascot — portrait" class="logo-img" loading="lazy" />
          </div>
          <div class="logo-cell logo-cell--c1">
            <img src="/groomo-logo-imgbasictext-wh.png" alt="GROOMO logo with tagline" class="logo-img" loading="lazy" />
          </div>
          <div class="logo-cell logo-cell--c2">
            <img src="/groomo-logo-basic-blu.png" alt="GROOMO wordmark" class="logo-img" loading="lazy" />
          </div>
          <div class="logo-cell logo-cell--c3">
            <img src="/groomo-logo-imgbasic-wh.png" alt="GROOMO logo with icon" class="logo-img" loading="lazy" />
          </div>
          <div class="logo-cell logo-cell--right">
            <img src="/groomoinstitut-logo-imgnavysku-wh-1.png" alt="GROOMO Institut logo" class="logo-img" loading="lazy" />
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="brand-hero-wrap">
          <div class="brand-hero-bg"></div>
          <p class="brand-hero-caption">Brand and e-shop created<br />out of love for dogs.</p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- 03 E-SHOP -->
      <section class="cs-section" id="s03">
        <h2 class="h2-mini sec-h2">E-shop also for professional dog owners</h2>
        <p class="body sec-text">GROOMO.cz was never meant to be just a classic store. Dominika wanted it to become a guide and advisor that even the most experienced breeders could turn to.</p>
        <p class="body sec-text">That is why, in addition to products, we have also created a blog where experts write and where topics that dog owners really need are addressed. The inspiration for this was both salon practice and a detailed analysis of keywords. The articles answer specific questions: <em>“What to do if a dog scratches itself?”</em> <em>“How to treat alopecia?”</em> <em>“How to prepare a dog for a show?”</em> <em>“How to travel with a dog?”</em></p>
        <div class="bloky-img-wrap">
          <img src="/groomo-bloky.png" alt="GROOMO.cz — e-shop categories: shampoos, conditioners, treats, advice and grooming courses" class="section-img" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- 04 INSTITUTE -->
      <section class="cs-section" id="s04">
        <h2 class="h2-mini sec-h2">GROOMO Institut</h2>
        <p class="body sec-text">The entire plan also includes a course section that offers training for professional groomers, but dog and cat owners are also trained here.</p>
        <div class="institut-split">
          <div class="institut-collage">
            <img src="/groomo-institut-v1.webp" alt="GROOMO Institut — grooming courses and training for dogs and cats" class="section-img" loading="lazy" />
          </div>
          <div class="institut-card-col">
            <img src="/institut.png" alt="GROOMO Institut — logo" class="section-img institut-card-img" loading="lazy" />
            <blockquote class="cs-quote">
              <p>“Thanks to the dedicated GROOMO institute page, my courses started running so quickly that I didn’t know where to start.”</p>
              <cite>— Dominika Elliot</cite>
            </blockquote>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- 05 SHOPIFY -->
      <section class="cs-section" id="s05">
        <h2 class="h2-mini sec-h2">Shopify and more</h2>
        <p class="body sec-text">We made a lot of design and functionality adjustments to the template — we changed the menu, added advanced product filtering, labels, all so that the e-shop team could handle the settings independently. The challenge was the number of brands and product subgroups. However, the biggest innovation is the <strong class="hl">filtering by dog breed</strong> — probably a unique feature. Just select the breed you own and the e-shop will recommend shampoos, brushes or treats that are ideal for a specific dog.</p>
        <blockquote class="cs-quote cs-quote--photo">
          <img src="/dominika.webp" alt="Dominika Elliot, owner of GROOMO.cz" class="quote-photo" loading="lazy" />
          <div class="quote-body">
            <p>“I wanted every owner to easily find what their dog needs. Thanks to filtering by breed, this is now possible.”</p>
            <cite>— Dominika Elliot</cite>
          </div>
        </blockquote>

        <!-- Tribe banner — belongs to the Shopify block -->
        <div class="tribe-banner">
          <img src="/najdi-sve-plemeno.webp" alt="GROOMO — find your breed, a row of various dog breeds" class="tribe-bg-img" loading="lazy" />
          <h3 class="tribe-label">Find<br />your breed</h3>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- 06 CONTENT -->
      <section class="cs-section" id="s06">
        <div class="content-split">
          <div class="content-text">
            <h2 class="h2-mini sec-h2">Content that helps and sells</h2>
            <p class="body sec-text">The new website is not just about products. From the beginning, GROOMO has positioned itself as a brand that shares experiences and offers help. Whether in the form of articles, advice from experts, or online courses.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="content-img content-img--card">
            <img src="/refka1.png" alt="Customer review of a shampoo on GROOMO.cz — Margita, 5 stars" class="section-img" loading="lazy" />
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- 07 RESULTS -->
      <section class="cs-section" id="s07">
        <div class="content-split">
          <div class="content-img content-img--card">
            <img src="/refka2.png" alt="Customer review of dried meat treats on GROOMO.cz — Natálie S., 5 stars" class="section-img" loading="lazy" />
          </div>
          <div class="content-text">
            <h2 class="h2-mini sec-h2">Price vs. performance — $$$</h2>
            <p class="body sec-text">The project was built with a strong focus on a reasonable budget from the start. Shopify, combined with custom customizations, allowed us to build an e-shop that felt almost like a custom solution, while still offering excellent value for money.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <h2 class="h2-mini sec-h2">Results</h2>
        <p class="body sec-text">The GROOMO e-shop was launched in November 2024. Within the first few weeks, it brought a lot of registrations and positive feedback from customers and professionals.</p>
        <p class="body sec-text">The biggest benefit was the filtering by breed, which makes shopping easier for owners and at the same time makes GROOMO an e-shop that has no equal on the Czech market.</p>

        <div class="zaver-card">
          <h2 class="h2-mini sec-h2">And conclusion?</h2>
          <p class="body sec-text">In the beginning, there was an idea that took shape after a few meetings. Within four months, thanks to the collaboration of the aethera team, it became a modern Shopify e-shop with a clear identity, unique features and content that helps owners and professionals alike.</p>
          <p class="body-maxi sec-text"><span class="hl">GROOMO is now a brand that connects products, education and experience</span> — and thanks to this, it has a unique place among dog e-shops.</p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- 08 GALLERY -->
      <section class="cs-section" id="s08">
        <h2 class="h2-mini sec-h2">Gallery</h2>
        <div class="gallery-grid">
          <a href="/hp-groomo-cz.png" class="gallery-item" data-index="0">
            <img src="/hp-groomo-cz.png" alt="GROOMO — e-shop homepage" class="gallery-img" loading="lazy" />
            <div class="gallery-overlay" aria-hidden="true"><svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8"><circle cx="11" cy="11" r="8"/><line x1="21" y1="21" x2="16.65" y2="16.65"/><line x1="11" y1="8" x2="11" y2="14"/><line x1="8" y1="11" x2="14" y2="11"/></svg></div>
          </a>
          <a href="/groomo-filter.webp" class="gallery-item" data-index="1">
            <img src="/groomo-filter.webp" alt="GROOMO — filtering by breed" class="gallery-img" loading="lazy" />
            <div class="gallery-overlay" aria-hidden="true"><svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8"><circle cx="11" cy="11" r="8"/><line x1="21" y1="21" x2="16.65" y2="16.65"/><line x1="11" y1="8" x2="11" y2="14"/><line x1="8" y1="11" x2="14" y2="11"/></svg></div>
          </a>
          <a href="/menu.png" class="gallery-item" data-index="2">
            <img src="/menu.png" alt="GROOMO — navigation" class="gallery-img" loading="lazy" />
            <div class="gallery-overlay" aria-hidden="true"><svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8"><circle cx="11" cy="11" r="8"/><line x1="21" y1="21" x2="16.65" y2="16.65"/><line x1="11" y1="8" x2="11" y2="14"/><line x1="8" y1="11" x2="14" y2="11"/></svg></div>
          </a>
          <a href="/podle-plemene-groomocz.png" class="gallery-item" data-index="3">
            <img src="/podle-plemene-groomocz.png" alt="GROOMO — breed selection" class="gallery-img" loading="lazy" />
            <div class="gallery-overlay" aria-hidden="true"><svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8"><circle cx="11" cy="11" r="8"/><line x1="21" y1="21" x2="16.65" y2="16.65"/><line x1="11" y1="8" x2="11" y2="14"/><line x1="8" y1="11" x2="14" y2="11"/></svg></div>
          </a>
          <a href="/moje-plemeno-in-black.png" class="gallery-item" data-index="4">
            <img src="/moje-plemeno-in-black.png" alt="GROOMO — my breed" class="gallery-img" loading="lazy" />
            <div class="gallery-overlay" aria-hidden="true"><svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8"><circle cx="11" cy="11" r="8"/><line x1="21" y1="21" x2="16.65" y2="16.65"/><line x1="11" y1="8" x2="11" y2="14"/><line x1="8" y1="11" x2="14" y2="11"/></svg></div>
          </a>
          <a href="/clanek-blog-groomo-cz.png" class="gallery-item" data-index="5">
            <img src="/clanek-blog-groomo-cz.png" alt="GROOMO — blog for dog owners" class="gallery-img" loading="lazy" />
            <div class="gallery-overlay" aria-hidden="true"><svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8"><circle cx="11" cy="11" r="8"/><line x1="21" y1="21" x2="16.65" y2="16.65"/><line x1="11" y1="8" x2="11" y2="14"/><line x1="8" y1="11" x2="14" y2="11"/></svg></div>
          </a>
        </div>
      </section>

    </main>
  </div>

  <!-- CTA — full width, outside grid -->
  <section class="cs-cta">
    <h2>Want a great e-shop too?<br />Get in touch!</h2>
    <div class="cta-links">
      <a href="mailto:info@aethero.cz" class="cta-link">info@aethero.cz</a>
      <a href="tel:+420776067663" class="cta-link">+420 776 067 663</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- LIGHTBOX -->
  <div id="lightbox" class="lightbox" aria-hidden="true" role="dialog" aria-modal="true" aria-label="Screenshot gallery">
    <button class="lightbox-close" aria-label="Close">✕</button>
    <button class="lightbox-prev" aria-label="Previous">&#8249;</button>
    <button class="lightbox-next" aria-label="Next">&#8250;</button>
    <img id="lightbox-img" src="" alt="" class="lightbox-img" />
    <div class="lightbox-counter" id="lightbox-counter"></div>
  </div>

</PageLayout>

<style>
  /* ─── 2-ROW × 2-COL LAYOUT ─── */
  .cs-layout {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 260px 1fr;
    grid-template-areas:
      ". hero-head"
      "aside main";
    column-gap: 80px;
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 160px var(--space-24) 80px;
  }
  .cs-hero-head {
    grid-area: hero-head;
    padding-bottom: var(--space-32);
  }
  .cs-aside {
    grid-area: aside;
    position: sticky;
    top: 88px;
    align-self: start;
  }
  .cs-main { grid-area: main; min-width: 0; }

  /* ─── TYPOGRAPHY ─── */
  .cs-label { margin-bottom: var(--space-24); }
  .cs-h1 {
    font-size: var(--fs-60); font-weight: 700; line-height: 1.15;
    color: #fff; margin-bottom: 0;
  }
  .cs-h1 .hl-name { color: var(--text-secondary); }

  /* Page nav (sticky TOC) */
  .page-nav {
    background: var(--card-button);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    padding: 16px;
    display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 8px;
  }
  .page-nav-item {
    font-family: var(--font-primary);
    font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7); text-transform: uppercase;
    text-decoration: none; padding: 4px 0;
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }
  .page-nav-item:hover { color: var(--action); }

  /* Perex */
  .cs-perex {
    font-family: var(--font-secondary); font-size: var(--fs-22);
    font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.65; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.85);
    max-width: 720px; margin: 0 0 var(--space-40);
  }

  /* ─── SECTIONS ─── */
  .cs-section { padding: var(--space-80) 0; background: var(--ae-bg-primary); }
  /* Content + Price/performance = review pair, closer together */
  #s06 { padding-bottom: var(--space-32); }
  #s07 { padding-top: var(--space-32); }
  /* Results + Conclusion = separate blocks with large spacing */
  #s07 > .sec-h2 { margin-top: var(--space-80); }

  /* Conclusion block — card with a soft lavender→teal gradient */
  .zaver-card {
    margin-top: var(--space-80);
    padding: var(--space-40);
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(160, 129, 209, 0.12), rgba(22, 190, 207, 0.05));
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.10);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
  }
  .zaver-card .sec-h2 { margin-top: 0; }
  .zaver-card > *:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }
  .sec-h2 { font-weight: 700; color: #fff; margin-bottom: var(--space-32); }
  .sec-h2--lav { color: var(--text-secondary); }
  .sec-text { margin-bottom: var(--space-24); max-width: 720px; }
  .sec-text .hl { color: #A081D1; font-weight: 700; }
  .section-img { width: 100%; height: auto; border-radius: var(--radius-md); display: block; }

  /* ─── 01 BRAND ─── */
  .brand-logo-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 0.85fr 1.3fr 0.85fr;
    grid-template-rows: repeat(3, 1fr);
    height: 400px;
    gap: 2px;
    background: #07051B;
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    overflow: hidden;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-40);
  }
  .logo-cell {
    background: #000326;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    padding: 24px 20px;
  }
  .logo-cell--left  { grid-column: 1; grid-row: 1 / 4; }
  .logo-cell--right { grid-column: 3; grid-row: 1 / 4; }
  .logo-cell--c1    { grid-column: 2; grid-row: 1; }
  .logo-cell--c2    { grid-column: 2; grid-row: 2; }
  .logo-cell--c3    { grid-column: 2; grid-row: 3; }
  .logo-img { width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: contain; display: block; }
  .logo-cell--left .logo-img,
  .logo-cell--right .logo-img { height: 100%; width: auto; max-width: 100%; }

  .brand-hero-wrap {
    position: relative; height: 300px; overflow: hidden;
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
  }
  .brand-hero-bg {
    position: absolute; inset: 0;
    background-image: url('/groomo-mainheader011.png');
    background-size: cover; background-position: center top;
  }
  .brand-hero-caption {
    position: absolute; top: 50%; left: 40px;
    transform: translateY(-50%);
    font-family: var(--font-primary); font-size: var(--fs-32);
    font-weight: 700; color: #fff; line-height: 1.25; margin: 0;
    text-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0,3,38,0.5);
    max-width: 340px;
  }

  /* ─── CONTENT SPLIT ─── */
  .content-split {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 48px; align-items: center;
  }
  .content-text .sec-h2 { margin-top: 0; }
  .content-img {
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    overflow: hidden; border-radius: var(--radius-md); max-height: 460px;
  }
  .content-img .section-img {
    width: 100%; height: 460px; object-fit: cover; object-position: top;
  }
  /* Review card — show whole, no crop */
  .content-img--card { max-height: none; }
  .content-img--card .section-img { height: auto; object-fit: contain; }

  /* Wide category collage (E-shop) — full column width */
  .bloky-img-wrap {
    margin-top: var(--space-40);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md); overflow: hidden;
  }
  .bloky-img-wrap .section-img { width: 100%; height: auto; }

  /* ─── INSTITUTE ─── */
  .institut-split {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 48px; align-items: start;
    margin-top: var(--space-40);
  }
  .institut-split .section-img { width: 100%; height: auto; }
  .institut-card-col { display: flex; flex-direction: column; }
  .institut-card-img {
    width: 100%;
    aspect-ratio: 16 / 9; object-fit: cover; object-position: center;
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
  }
  .institut-card-col .cs-quote { margin-top: var(--space-64); }

  /* ─── QUOTE — light, borderless emphasis (decorative glyph + soft glow) ─── */
  .cs-quote {
    position: relative;
    margin: var(--space-40) 0 0;
    max-width: 660px;
    padding: calc(var(--space-16) + 10px) 0 0 calc(var(--space-40) + 10px);
  }
  .cs-quote::before {
    content: '\201E';
    position: absolute; top: -0.42em; left: -0.06em;
    font-family: var(--font-serif); font-style: italic; font-weight: 400;
    font-size: var(--fs-100); line-height: 1;
    color: var(--text-secondary); opacity: 0.9;
    text-shadow: 0 0 28px rgba(160, 129, 209, 0.5);
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .cs-quote p {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: var(--fs-24); font-style: italic;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.9); line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: var(--space-16);
  }
  .cs-quote cite {
    font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.55);
    font-weight: 600; display: block;
  }

  /* Quote with photo (testimonial) — 1/3 photo : 2/3 quote; no glyph (photo is the anchor) */
  .cs-quote--photo {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 2fr;
    gap: var(--space-40); align-items: center;
    padding: 0; max-width: none;
  }
  .cs-quote--photo::before { content: none; }
  .quote-photo {
    width: 100%; height: auto; aspect-ratio: 1 / 1;
    border-radius: var(--radius-md); object-fit: cover; object-position: top;
  }
  .cs-quote--photo .quote-body p:last-of-type { margin-bottom: var(--space-8); }

  /* ─── TRIBE BANNER ─── */
  .tribe-banner {
    position: relative;
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    overflow: hidden;
    margin: var(--space-40) 0 0;
  }
  .tribe-bg-img { width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; }
  .tribe-label {
    position: absolute; top: 50%; left: 48px;
    transform: translateY(-50%);
    font-family: var(--font-primary);
    font-size: var(--fs-36); font-weight: 700;
    color: #fff; line-height: 1.1;
    margin: 0;
  }

  /* ─── GALLERY ─── */
  .gallery-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: var(--space-16);
    grid-auto-rows: 240px;
  }
  .gallery-item {
    display: block; position: relative;
    overflow: hidden; border-radius: var(--radius-sm); cursor: zoom-in;
  }
  .gallery-img {
    width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; object-position: top;
    display: block; transition: transform 0.4s ease;
  }
  .gallery-item:hover .gallery-img { transform: scale(1.04); }
  .gallery-overlay {
    position: absolute; inset: 0;
    background: rgba(0, 3, 38, 0.5);
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    color: #fff; opacity: 0; transition: opacity 0.22s;
  }
  .gallery-item:hover .gallery-overlay { opacity: 1; }

  /* ─── LIGHTBOX (per-page, scrollable for tall screenshots) ─── */
  .lightbox {
    display: none; position: fixed; inset: 0; z-index: 9999;
    background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.92); overflow: auto;
    padding: 64px 24px; cursor: zoom-out;
  }
  .lightbox.is-open { display: block; }
  .lightbox-img {
    display: block; margin: 0 auto;
    width: auto; max-width: min(1000px, 92vw); height: auto;
    border-radius: var(--radius-md); cursor: default;
    box-shadow: 0 20px 80px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);
  }
  .lightbox-close {
    position: fixed; top: 20px; right: 20px;
    background: none; border: 2px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
    color: #fff; font-size: 20px; width: 48px; height: 48px;
    border-radius: 50%; cursor: pointer; line-height: 1;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    transition: border-color 0.2s; z-index: 2;
  }
  .lightbox-close:hover { border-color: #fff; }
  .lightbox-prev, .lightbox-next {
    position: fixed; top: 50%; transform: translateY(-50%);
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12); border: none; color: #fff;
    font-size: 44px; line-height: 1; width: 60px; height: 60px;
    border-radius: 50%; cursor: pointer; z-index: 2;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    transition: background 0.2s;
  }
  .lightbox-prev { left: 24px; }
  .lightbox-next { right: 24px; }
  .lightbox-prev:hover, .lightbox-next:hover { background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.28); }
  .lightbox-counter {
    position: fixed; bottom: 20px; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%);
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.55);
    font-family: var(--font-primary); font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.08em;
  }

  /* ─── CTA ─── */
  .cs-cta { padding: var(--space-120) var(--space-24); background: var(--action); text-align: center; }
  .cs-cta h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-primary); font-size: var(--fs-70);
    font-weight: 700; color: #fff; line-height: 1.2; margin-bottom: var(--space-40);
  }
  .cta-links { display: flex; gap: var(--space-40); justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .cta-link {
    font-family: var(--font-primary); font-size: var(--fs-40);
    font-weight: 700; color: var(--ae-straight-blue); text-decoration: none;
  }
  .cta-link:hover { text-decoration: underline; text-underline-offset: 4px; }

  /* ─── RESPONSIVE ─── */
  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .cs-layout {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      grid-template-areas: "hero-head" "main";
      padding-top: 120px;
    }
    .cs-aside { display: none; }
  }
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .content-split { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: var(--space-40); }
    .institut-split { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: var(--space-40); }
    .cs-quote--photo { flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-start; gap: var(--space-24); }
    .tribe-label { font-size: var(--fs-28); left: 24px; }
    .gallery-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; grid-auto-rows: 180px; }
  }
</style>

<script>
  const lb = document.getElementById('lightbox');
  const lbImg = document.getElementById('lightbox-img');
  const lbCounter = document.getElementById('lightbox-counter');
  const items = [...document.querySelectorAll('.gallery-item')];
  const images = items.map(item => ({
    src: item.getAttribute('href'),
    alt: item.querySelector('img')?.alt || ''
  }));
  let current = 0;

  function show(index) {
    current = (index + images.length) % images.length;
    lbImg.src = images[current].src;
    lbImg.alt = images[current].alt;
    lbCounter.textContent = `${current + 1} / ${images.length}`;
    lb.scrollTop = 0;
  }
  function openLightbox(index) {
    show(index);
    lb.classList.add('is-open');
    lb.setAttribute('aria-hidden', 'false');
    document.body.style.overflow = 'hidden';
  }
  function closeLightbox() {
    lb.classList.remove('is-open');
    lb.setAttribute('aria-hidden', 'true');
    lbImg.src = '';
    document.body.style.overflow = '';
  }

  items.forEach((item, i) => {
    item.addEventListener('click', e => { e.preventDefault(); openLightbox(i); });
  });

  lb.querySelector('.lightbox-close').addEventListener('click', closeLightbox);
  lb.querySelector('.lightbox-prev').addEventListener('click', e => { e.stopPropagation(); show(current - 1); });
  lb.querySelector('.lightbox-next').addEventListener('click', e => { e.stopPropagation(); show(current + 1); });
  lb.addEventListener('click', e => { if (e.target === lb) closeLightbox(); });
  document.addEventListener('keydown', e => {
    if (!lb.classList.contains('is-open')) return;
    if (e.key === 'Escape') closeLightbox();
    if (e.key === 'ArrowLeft') show(current - 1);
    if (e.key === 'ArrowRight') show(current + 1);
  });
</script>
